ntor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"f5b1663\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-b4dbb67\" data-id=\"b4dbb67\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7925546 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7925546\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Strengthening relationships  \n\nby helping people see God, themselves, and others   in new ways.  <\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b355401 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b355401\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Synergy [<i>\u03c3\u03c5\u03bd\u03b5\u03c1\u03b3\u03af\u03b1<\/i>, Gr.;<i> synergia<\/i>, Lat.]:<i> <\/i><\/b>the interaction of two or more agents or forces so that their combined effect is greater than the sum of their individual effects; from the Greek word <i>\u03c3\u03c5\u03bd\u03b5\u03c1\u03b3\u03cc\u03c2<\/i>, meaning &#8220;working together.&#8221; <\/span><\/p><p>Since 1982 I have served in Christian ministry as pastor\/priest, missionary, missions administrator, and seminary professor. My wife and I have lived and served as members of evangelical Protestant and Orthodox Christian communities in various parts of the world. I know intimately the temptations and sufferings that accompany servant-leadership in the Church. I also know the victories and joys of Christian ministry!<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-ece2c5d\" data-id=\"ece2c5d\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7289b91 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"7289b91\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"703\" src=\"https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/David-Rozanne-3-1024x900.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-561\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/David-Rozanne-3-1024x900.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/David-Rozanne-3-300x264.jpg 300w, https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/David-Rozanne-3-768x675.jpg 768w, https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/David-Rozanne-3-1536x1350.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/David-Rozanne-3-2048x1800.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-191f8c8 elementor-reverse-tablet elementor-reverse-mobile elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"191f8c8\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-4e2bae6\" data-id=\"4e2bae6\" data-element_type=\"column